March 2011 (&#8220;Pillay condemns Libyan Security Forces violence against journalists&#8221;), and on 20 April 
</p>
<p>2011 (&#8220;Libya&#8223;s indiscriminate attacks on civilians in Misrata may be international crimes&#8221;). 
