</p>
<p> 101 Tim Hetherington, 40, was a seasoned photojournalist who contributed photographs to American 
magazine Vanity Fair. He directed <i>Restrepo</i>, an acclaimed 2010 documentary film about fighting in 
Afghanistan, which was nominated for an Oscar.  
